	<h1 class="title">除了中国人最喜欢买买买，全球奢侈品市场的变化还有这 14 个有趣的事</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/399912/small/399912.JPG?1452046699" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">张田小 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-10-30 16:26:48 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/16851/medium/16851.jpg?1446189330" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


